<span id=actions-account-module></span><h1 id='actions-account-module-'>Actions.Account Module</h1>
<p><strong>Actions</strong> - ACT_ACCOUNT_ classes <strong>account for</strong> (detect, count &amp; report) various DCS events occuring on <a href="#unit-module-">Unit</a>s.</p>

