<span id=act_account_deads-class></span><h2 id='act_account_deads-class-'>ACT_ACCOUNT_DEADS Class</h2>
<pre>
Inheritance : The ACT_ACCOUNT_DEADS Class inherits from the following parents :
BASE
    `-- FSM
        `-- FSM_CONTROLLABLE
            `-- FSM_PROCESS
                `-- ACT_ACCOUNT
                    `-- ACT_ACCOUNT_DEADS
</pre>

<p>The ACT_ACCOUNT_DEADS class accounts (detects, counts and reports) successful kills of DCS units.
The process is given a <a href="#set-module-">Set</a> of units that will be tracked upon successful destruction.
The process will end after each target has been successfully destroyed.
Each successful dead will trigger an Account state transition that can be scored, modified or administered.</p>
